      <title>波兰最大反对党因选举融资被罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/poland-s-biggest-opposition-party-fined-over-election-financing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰选举委员会对前执政党法律与公正党处以罚款，原因是该党在去年大选中挪用公款以赢得胜利，这对民族主义反对派团体造成了重大打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/poland-s-biggest-opposition-party-fined-over-election-financing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 17:06:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>艾伯塔省人口激增，油价上涨导致盈余增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/alberta-sees-population-boom-higher-oil-prices-boosting-surplus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于油价高于预期以及人口激增带来更多税收收入，阿尔伯塔省预计本财年结束时的盈余将高于之前预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/alberta-sees-population-boom-higher-oil-prices-boosting-surplus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 17:02:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管没有新总理，马克龙的支持率仍然上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/macron-popularity-rises-even-in-absence-of-new-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BVA Xsight 的一项民意调查显示，尽管法国总统在提前举行议会选举后未能任命新总理，但埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的支持率仍有所上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/macron-popularity-rises-even-in-absence-of-new-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 16:51:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>陆军为与特朗普团队对峙的阿灵顿公墓工作人员辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/army-defends-cemetery-staffer-who-confronted-trump-s-team</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国陆军为一名在参观阿灵顿国家公墓期间与唐纳德·特朗普竞选团队发生冲突的工作人员辩护，称她被“突然推到一边”，然后在事件发生后遭到“不公平的攻击”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/army-defends-cemetery-staffer-who-confronted-trump-s-team</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 16:17:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊与沙特协调避免红海油轮灾难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/greece-saudi-arabia-coordinate-to-avert-oil-tanker-disaster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，希腊正在牵头清空并拖走上周在红海遭到袭击的一艘油轮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/greece-saudi-arabia-coordinate-to-avert-oil-tanker-disaster</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 16:12:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃伦敦促华尔街监管机构解释执法行动减少的原因</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/warren-presses-wall-street-regulator-to-explain-decline-in-enforcement-actions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议员伊丽莎白·沃伦 (Elizabeth Warren) 正在向美国经纪交易商监管机构 Finra 施压，要求其说明为何近年来执法数量大幅下降，而 Finra 的成功正是将不良行为者驱逐出行业的关键。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/warren-presses-wall-street-regulator-to-explain-decline-in-enforcement-actions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多的保守党对手承诺减缓加拿大人口增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/trudeau-s-tory-rival-pledges-to-slow-canada-s-population-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守党领袖皮埃尔·波利耶夫 (Pierre Poilievre) 目前被认为是下届加拿大大选的获胜热门人选，他表示，加拿大需要减缓人口增长速度，以更好地适应住房、就业和医疗保健的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/trudeau-s-tory-rival-pledges-to-slow-canada-s-population-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 15:46:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度第二艘弹道导弹潜艇加入舰队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/india-inducts-second-ballistic-missile-submarine-into-fleet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度国防部在一份声明中表示，印度海军舰队于周四将第二艘核动力弹道导弹潜艇投入服役。这一进展将增强印度从海、空或陆发射核武器的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/india-inducts-second-ballistic-missile-submarine-into-fleet</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 15:45:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称将宣布一项计划，让美国成为“加密之都”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/trump-says-he-ll-announce-a-plan-to-make-us-the-crypto-capital-of-the-planet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普似乎正在更深入地涉足数字资产世界，他表示将公布计划，确保美国成为“全球加密之都”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/trump-says-he-ll-announce-a-plan-to-make-us-the-crypto-capital-of-the-planet</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 14:50:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将对每架缺乏升级的 F-35 扣留 500 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/us-withholding-5-million-for-each-f-35-lacking-full-upgrade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国防部 F-35 项目办公室表示，对于每架尚未配备符合规格的先进硬件和软件的 F-35 飞机，五角大楼将向洛克希德马丁公司扣留 500 万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/us-withholding-5-million-for-each-f-35-lacking-full-upgrade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 14:40:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
